channel.title: MESG Engine: A New Era
channel.description:
We’re currently in the first stage of our deployment and are proud to announce that Version 0.1 of our software, Engine, has launched and is available for use now.

This is a companion discussion topic for the original entry at https://blog.mesg.com/mesg-core-v0-1-launch-a-new-era/
